@startuml
title PatientJourney Lifecycle

state ACTIVE
state SUSPENDED
state COMPLETED

[*] --> ACTIVE
ACTIVE --> SUSPENDED : "suspend"
SUSPENDED --> ACTIVE : "resume"
ACTIVE --> COMPLETED : "complete"
SUSPENDED --> COMPLETED : "complete"

note right
  The codebase currently defines the enum but lacks enforced transitions
end note

@enduml
